reviewText: It was for a friend. She enjoyed it.
This dvd was timely and it is good old school preaching. We need more preaching like this. I am truly fed every time I listen to this preacher.(smile)

The late B.W. Smith was a great preacher.  I first learned about while overseas in Korea.  His message was awe inspiring and I am sure his church in Buffalo NY still miss him today.  But God's word lives on!
